---
import Button from '@/components/shared/Button.astro';
import SectionHeader from '@/components/shared/SectionHeader.astro';
import classes from '@/data/styles.json';
---

<section class="bg-background-secondary py-24" id="about">
  <div class={classes.container}>
    <div class="flex flex-row gap-8">
      <div class="w-1/3">
        <SectionHeader preHeading="Customer Obsession" heading={['Building for', 'real people.']} />
        <p class={classes.secondaryText}>
          It’s about the person on the other side of the screen, not just the browser. To me, code
          is just a tool to make someone’s day a little easier. I sweat the technical details—like
          speed and accessibility—so the user gets a smooth, frustration-free experience every time.
        </p>
        <div class="pt-4">
          <Button style="tertiary" href="/profile"> More about my process </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid w-2/3 grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div
          class="border-border-tertiary bg-card-primary transform rounded-2xl border p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          <span class="text-primary material-symbols-outlined mb-4 text-3xl dark:text-white"
            >bolt</span
          >
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-bold">Inclusive Design</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary-text text-sm leading-relaxed dark:text-gray-400">
            Building universally accessible interfaces with strict WCAG 2.1 compliance and semantic
            HTML foundations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="border-border-tertiary bg-card-primary rounded-2xl border p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 md:mt-12"
        >
          <span class="text-primary material-symbols-outlined mb-4 text-3xl dark:text-white"
            >accessibility_new</span
          >
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-bold">Performance</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary-text text-sm leading-relaxed dark:text-gray-400">
            Architecting for speed via Core Web Vitals optimization, intelligent code-splitting, and
            efficient asset delivery.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="border-border-tertiary bg-card-primary rounded-2xl border p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          <span class="text-primary material-symbols-outlined mb-4 text-3xl dark:text-white"
            >grid_view</span
          >
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-bold">Design Fidelity</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary-text text-sm leading-relaxed dark:text-gray-400">
            Bridging the gap between creative and engineering to deliver pixel-perfect, responsive
            UI that matches the vision.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="border-border-tertiary bg-card-primary rounded-2xl border p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 md:mt-12"
        >
          <span class="text-primary material-symbols-outlined mb-4 text-3xl dark:text-white"
            >integration_instructions</span
          >
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-bold">Scalable Architecture</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary-text text-sm leading-relaxed dark:text-gray-400">
            Leveraging TypeScript and modular patterns to build robust, maintainable systems that
            support rapid growth.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
